## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of how dementia leads to social isolation. The impact of cultural, geographical, and individual differences on social isolation in dementia patients was not extensively covered. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of the COVID-19 pandemic means that some data may have changed since the time of publication. Further research is needed to explore long-term solutions to mitigate social isolation in dementia patients.